Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}To sink or swim {\fsp1}生き残るために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.97,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}dog eat dog world {\fsp1}だと言い聞かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:23.81,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}What went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:26.77,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Survival of the fittest {\fsp1}弱肉強食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:28.60,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}If it's the world that our wisdom will lead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:33.78,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}Then tell me what went wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.32,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I've paid my dues
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:38.11,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}I've sold my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:41.99,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}So tell me, what is left for me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.16,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}when I've given up everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.71,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　どう描いてたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:54.21,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}どの景色を見ても　何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.80,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:04.47,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}あの景色を求めていた　僕は今無感情なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.89,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　どう描いてたんだろう？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:14.44,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}どの景色を見ても　何も感じなくなったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.99,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ねぇ　考え直しても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:24.58,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}あの景色を求めていた　僕は今無感情なの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.12,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}真実の見えない世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:29.62,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}善と悪のバランスを保ち
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.13,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}殺すか殺されるかの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.67,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}ちっぽけな世界なのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:40.51,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp1}おい　誰か答えてみてくれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:42.51,op-jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是沉是浮 为了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:18.97,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉他 这是同类相残的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.97,0:01:23.81,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:26.77,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2)}适者生存 弱肉强食
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.77,0:01:28.60,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果智慧能引领这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:33.78,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那就告诉我 为什么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.78,0:01:36.32,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已付出太多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:38.11,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已出卖灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:41.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}告诉我 如果我放弃一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:44.16,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}又能够得到些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:47.71,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 这是个怎样的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:54.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看过太多风景 却毫无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:57.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 我已思考无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:02:04.47,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了追寻那个风景 我是否已毫无感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:07.89,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 这是个怎样的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:14.44,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我看过太多风景 却毫无感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:17.99,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我 我已思考无数次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:24.58,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}为了追寻那个风景 我是否已毫无感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:27.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看不见真相的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.12,0:02:29.62,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}维持善恶的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.62,0:02:32.13,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}杀或被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:34.67,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}这世界难道这么无趣吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:40.51,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}喂 谁能回答我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.51,0:02:40.51,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:23:01.49,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}It's just like a burning torch in a storm
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:07.16,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}like a little flower blooming in a home
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:12.81,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}強く確かな意思をかかげ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:18.18,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}時に優しくあればいい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:24.98,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}A misty moon
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:30.73,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}I'm missing you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:39.92,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}滲む景色に膝を抱き　胸をはせる時
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:45.70,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}Listen to me. Sail away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:51.65,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,300)}未開の海に　海路を照らす　願い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:59.32,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,700)}つないだ声は　答えのない世界へと帆を揺らす
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:08.04,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,700)}You're not alone　ただ　荒波をゆけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:13.70,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,700)}その闇を抜け
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:13.70,ed-jp,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.62,0:23:01.49,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}你如风暴中燃烧的火把
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:07.16,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}亦如房间里绽放的小花
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.52,0:23:12.81,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}愿你坚韧不拔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:18.18,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}时而柔情似水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.14,0:23:24.98,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}朦胧月光下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.98,0:23:30.73,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}我思念着你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:39.92,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(700,700)}我于美景中抱膝而坐 思绪万千
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.92,0:23:45.70,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,0)}听我说 再次远航吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:51.65,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(0,300)}将你的航路 延伸进未拓的海域 许下心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.65,0:23:59.32,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,700)}我们的声音 将朝着那没有答案的世界 扬帆起航
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:08.04,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,700)}你不是孤身一人 乘风破浪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.04,0:24:13.70,ed-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(300,700)}冲破黑暗吧
